Assemblies under trees, minutes kept in school notebooks, the CNC's men watching from a pickup across the road. The official central offers credit and delivers debt; Danzós offers nothing and delivers Danzós, which in the Yaqui valley still counts for more.

@danzos_tierra
title: Tomas de tierra
subtitle: The Constitution promises land. Occupy some of it and invite the Constitution to catch up.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; sup_peasants += 8; represion += 3; expediente += 3; fac_ortodoxos += 2; fac_renovadores -= 1; fac_nueva_izquierda -= 1

Before dawn the fences come down and the white flags of the *solicitantes* go up on land the paperwork has owed them for thirty years. Sometimes the state negotiates. Sometimes it sends the judiciales, and the Party's lawyers meet the survivors. Either way, the valley learns which side the Party stands on, fence by fence.
